              <tr><td><strong>Paid acquisition</strong></td><td>Buy traffic, measure LTV vs CAC</td><td>Days</td><td class="cell-meh">Linear — scales with budget only</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Product-led growth</strong></td><td>Product itself drives acquisition</td><td>Months to years</td><td class="cell-yes">High — no marginal cost per user</td></tr>
